          }
        },
        {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "I'm an OECM buyer. What do I include in my quote request?",
            "answer": "<p>Mention that you're purchasing under OECM and include your organisation's OECM member number. Brant Business Interiors holds Agreement 2025-470 in the office furniture category. We'll format the quote against pre-tendered pricing and flag which line items are OECM-eligible so your purchasing team can approve it cleanly — no extra steps on your end.</p><p>Not sure if your organisation is OECM-eligible? <a href='/pages/oecm'>See our OECM overview</a> or call 1-800-835-9565 and we'll confirm in five minutes.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you include delivery and installation in quotes?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes — all quotes include delivery and installation as a separate line item so you can see the full landed cost. We deliver across Ontario and can install with our own crew. After-hours and weekend installs are available for occupied spaces. For out-of-province shipments, call us for a freight quote.</p>"
          }
        },
